{"tid":1161804,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姚子羚要脅Raymond二揀一 大婆蔡宛珊承認前夫曾想復合","createTime":"2019-05-19T12:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T12:48:45.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c65b03d163b8539c175934527c823277811bbf5e","tid":1161804,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"姚子羚今日爆出疑搶人老公，與夜店董事Raymond拍拖。而Raymond的正印太太蔡宛珊(Sarika)今日接受《蘋果》電話訪問，透露與Raymond於2017年1月已經開始分居，並於今年1月正式離婚。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》今日再收到另一位讀者爆料，稱Raymond與Sarika在分居期間，一直希望氹回Sarika，堅拒簽紙，所以拖拉很久，而姚子羚亦曾要脅Raymond：「唔簽紙不如同番你老婆一齊！」Sarika在電話中想了一會說：「er...都係(有氹)，所以我冇理。至於佢哋所有detail ，我就冇問，唔想特別講或comment，同老公分開之後，我唔會理、唔參與、唔過問佢嘅感情事。」<br />\n<br />\nSarika承認與姚子羚是認識，但不是深交，她說﹕「係朋友同朋友間認識，問番佢哋，識佢時純朋友同朋友，不太friend。」追問是分居前還是分居後認識，Sarika沒有正面回答。<br />\n<br />\n問到分手是否很傷心？Sarika說﹕「我哋拍拖4年，結婚至分居6年，一齊都10年。我哋一齊有層樓、有貓，分開後都有好多事要處理，所以係有聯絡。但最唔開心時候都過咗，現在我係單身，好開心簽咗棋人，阿Bob好錫我，又喺ViuTV做節目，現在都係專注工作，我好感恩好多人支持我，我都會堅強。」"},{"pid":"911362bd8bfac955677b8fe723ab8767196c702c","tid":1161804,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:20:52.000Z","msg":"【獨家訪問】傳子羚要脅Raymond二揀一 大婆蔡宛珊承認前夫曾想復合<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190519&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59619068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190519%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59619068&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=ac3c1d0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190519%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59619068&h=eb6d050b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190519&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59619068</a>"},{"pid":"653f8aefee8f8030209801ad4ea0977e8710f9f0","tid":1161804,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:21:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Raymond的正印太太蔡宛珊(Sarika)今日接受《蘋果》電話訪問，透露與Raymond於2017年1月已經開始分居，並於今年1月正式離婚。<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e283f02988cccb0d9a512470fb183635d30a5a76","tid":1161804,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"子羚好無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508bfb9904249497f04e132e4e6442bdee47ac2f","tid":1161804,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"全城炒車"},{"pid":"6eb5fcf194a5e92ae9aec230bd6ca6fa11bb0779","tid":1161804,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05dcc391b655543efb83fc8293071de51195086","tid":1161804,"uid":144275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:33:01.000Z","msg":"個老公一定塞左好多錢比大婆叫佢唔好亂講野"},{"pid":"796395b52649b5189d6bc45c53a4b9b63555b520","tid":1161804,"uid":144275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:34:26.000Z","msg":"所以批相應該係二奶賣比蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbe10f4045d4d8862779b10601540afb4324813","tid":1161804,"uid":1430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"796395b52649b5189d6bc45c53a4b9b63555b520","tid":1161804,"uid":144275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:34:26.000Z","msg":"所以批相應該係二奶賣比蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"D相都係幫二奶打格仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5177dd0f765924e4e6eceb591bf582e48b8e82f2","tid":1161804,"uid":56716,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:43:43.000Z","msg":"咁叫要脅？表哥想要名份好正常，唔離婚咪同返老婆一齊囉，條仔拖泥帶水想享齊人之福仲想將責任卸落表哥度？"},{"pid":"4c6f013454ba4a57a7f2e68febeeac56fe51cf0b","tid":1161804,"uid":62655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"s